Unsaved Files Dialog Box

Requires: Professional System

This dialog box appears if you click the OK button in the Source Control Operations dialog box and a LabVIEW file type included in the source control operation has unsaved changes.

This dialog prompts you to save changes before completing a source control operation.

This dialog box includes the following components:

  • Files with unsaved changes—Lists the files included in the source control operation that have unsaved changes.
  • List unsaved changes—Launches the Explain Changes dialog box.
